@chapter GnomeCanvasGroup
Canvas item group

@section Overview
A canvas item that groups other canvas items. A canvas group is used for
organization, determining drawing stacking order, and for applying transforms on
all items in the group.

The @code{<gnome-canvas>} widget contains a toplevel "root" group which can be
queried with a call to @code{gnome-canvas-root}.

